# Forhemit Monorepo Environment Variables
#
# Each app has its own .env.example with detailed instructions:
# - apps/admin/.env.example       — Admin CRM (Clerk, Convex, UploadThing, etc.)
# - apps/marketing/.env.example   — Marketing site (Convex, UploadThing, Resend)
# - packages/convex/.env.example  — Convex backend (deployment, auth config)
#
# Quick start:
# 1. Copy each .env.example to .env.local
# 2. Fill in your actual values
# 3. Run `pnpm dev` to start all apps
